data.description:
Welcome to this stunning 5-bedroom, 3 full bath and 1/2 bath home! Step inside and be captivated by the gorgeous upgraded light fixtures that illuminate the home. The main floor features a stylish office with French doors. This home adds uniqueness with modern wood accent walls throughout the home.
The kitchen boasts beautiful granite countertops, a double oven, and stainless steel appliances, along with a charming breakfast nook to enjoy meals.
Upstairs, you'll find a huge loft area, perfect for relaxation or entertainment.
Outside, an awning covers the back porch, providing a shaded oasis for relaxation and gatherings. The community amenities include a refreshing pool and splash pad, making it an ideal place to unwind and create lasting memories.
Conveniently located near popular restaurants and grocery stores, and situated in a sought-after subdivision, this home offers the perfect blend of luxury, comfort, and convenience. 
What more can you ask for?!?
Don't miss the chance to make this dream home yours!
